title: Google seems smitten with its boring Pixel cases, as they’ll return for Pixel 6a
content:
Google threw away its fabric cases with the Pixel 5a and the Pixel 6 series, and it seems the replacement is sticking around. Like last year’s lineup, the Pixel 6a will get a set of pretty boring official cases.

more…

description: Google seems to be sticking with its boring, easy to discolor Pixel cases for the upcoming Pixel 6a, much to our dismay.
